WEBVTT

18:37.000 --> 18:38.020 line:80%
What's wrong, Mrs. Wang?

18:38.020 --> 18:40.080 line:80%
Did a rich relative visit your place?

18:40.160 --> 18:40.790 line:80%
Why?

18:40.830 --> 18:41.800 line:80%
I just saw the carriage

18:41.800 --> 18:43.350 line:80%
that left your house.

18:43.350 --> 18:46.610 line:80%
It was even grander
than the Song family's when they moved.
